==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ripping panel
<hw>Ripping panel</hw>. <fld>(Aeronautics)</fld> <def>A long patch, on a
balloon, to be ripped off, by the <er>rip cord</er>, at landing, in
order to allow the immediate escape of gas and instant deflation of the
bag.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ripping strip</ent>⟦br⟧
